{
  "id": "moat_analyzer",
  "name": "Economic Moat Analyzer",
  "trigger_phrases": [
    "analyze moat",
    "economic moat",
    "competitive advantage",
    "moat analysis for {symbol}",
    "competitive position"
  ],
  "description": "Deep analysis of a company's economic moat",
  "category": "analysis",
  "priority": 85,
  "workflow": [
    {
      "step": "load_moat_framework",
      "action": "knowledge_lookup",
      "parameters": {
        "knowledge_file": "buffett_framework.json",
        "section": "economic_moat"
      }
    },
    {
      "step": "analyze_brand",
      "action": "evaluate",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "brand_moat",
        "checks": [
          "premium_pricing_ability",
          "customer_loyalty",
          "mind_share_leadership"
        ]
      },
      "outputs": ["brand_score"]
    },
    {
      "step": "analyze_network",
      "action": "evaluate",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "network_effects",
        "checks": [
          "value_increases_with_users",
          "high_switching_costs",
          "winner_take_all_dynamics"
        ]
      },
      "outputs": ["network_score"]
    },
    {
      "step": "analyze_costs",
      "action": "evaluate",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "cost_advantages",
        "checks": [
          "lowest_cost_producer",
          "economies_of_scale",
          "unique_assets"
        ]
      },
      "outputs": ["cost_score"]
    },
    {
      "step": "analyze_switching",
      "action": "evaluate",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "switching_costs",
        "checks": [
          "painful_to_switch",
          "embedded_in_operations",
          "long_term_contracts"
        ]
      },
      "outputs": ["switching_score"]
    },
    {
      "step": "calculate_roic",
      "action": "calculate",
      "parameters": {
        "formula": "ROIC - WACC spread",
        "target": ">15% for wide moat"
      },
      "outputs": ["roic_spread"]
    },
    {
      "step": "overall_assessment",
      "action": "synthesize",
      "parameters": {
        "scores": [
          "{brand_score}",
          "{network_score}",
          "{cost_score}",
          "{switching_score}",
          "{roic_spread}"
        ]
      },
      "outputs": ["moat_rating", "moat_durability"]
    }
  ],
  "response": {
    "template": "ğŸ° **Economic Moat Analysis for {symbol}**\n\nğŸ“Š **Moat Sources Evaluation**\n\nğŸ·ï¸ **Brand Moat**: {brand_score}/10\n{brand_details}\n\nğŸŒ **Network Effects**: {network_score}/10\n{network_details}\n\nğŸ’° **Cost Advantages**: {cost_score}/10\n{cost_details}\n\nğŸ”’ **Switching Costs**: {switching_score}/10\n{switching_details}\n\nğŸ“ˆ **Financial Evidence**\nâ€¢ ROIC-WACC Spread: {roic_spread}%\nâ€¢ Gross Margin Stability: {margin_stability}\nâ€¢ 10-Year Avg ROIC: {avg_roic}%\n\nğŸ¯ **Overall Moat Rating**: {moat_rating}\nâ€¢ Width: {moat_width}\nâ€¢ Durability: {moat_durability}\nâ€¢ Trend: {moat_trend}\n\nğŸ’¡ **Investment Implications**\n{investment_action}",
    "format": "markdown"
  }
}